GENETIC_CODE_TABLES

public static final java.lang.String[] GENETIC_CODE_TABLES
Standard genetic code tables from GENBANK Nucleotides go A, C, G, T - Note: this is not the order used by the Genbank web site With the first codon position most significant (i.e. AAA, AAC, AAG, AAT, ACA, etc.).
